Code 1

class Solution {
    public boolean isOneBitCharacter(int[] bits) {
        int i = 0;

        while (i < bits.length - 1) {
            if (bits[i] == 1) {
                i++;
            } 
            i++;
        }

        return i == bits.length - 1;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O()
Space Compelxity : O()

